-- Dolans in talks to take Cablevision private: report
-- 
-- Tue May 1, 2007 7:26pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/01/us-cablevision-dolans-idUSN0126731720070501

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - The Dolan family, which controls Cablevision Systems Corp. ( CVC.N ), was in advanced talks with the Long Island, New York, cable operator to take the company private, The Wall Street Journal reported on Tuesday, citing a person familiar with the matter. 

 The family has made at least two earlier offers to buy the company in the past few years. Cablevision declined to comment.